  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Selection of the Basic Data Set of Financial Objects</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page topic  - topic-topic \" id=\"loio590ada531198434de10000000a174cb4\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Selection of the Basic Data Set of Financial Objects</h1><div class=\"body\">\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Use\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Use</h2>\n\n<p class=\"p\">When selecting the basic data set, the system takes into account the category of the\ndetermination procedure (counterparty/issuer risk), and the value date you entered.</p>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Integration\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Integration</h2>\n\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Selection criteria for counterparty/issuer risk determination procedures:</p><ol class=\"ol\">\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">a. In the default risk limit part of the financial object, you need to have set the\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Counterparty Risk Active</span> indicator.</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">b. If the fields <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Transaction Start CPR</span> and\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Transaction End CPR</span> in the financial object are filled, the\nvaluation data must be within this time period (up to and including these\ndates).</p></li>\n</ol></li>\n</ul>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Example\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Example</h2>\n\n<p class=\"p\">The following table explains the selection criteria:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrapper tablenoborder\"><table summary=\"\" class=\"table\" frame=\"border\" border=\"1\" rules=\"all\"><colgroup><col width=\"20%\"><col width=\"20%\"><col width=\"20%\"><col width=\"20%\"><col width=\"20%\"></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d247466e162\"><p class=\"p\">Valuation date</p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d247466e168\"><p class=\"p\">Transaction start</p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d247466e174\"><p class=\"p\">Transaction end</p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d247466e180\"><p class=\"p\">Counterparty relevant</p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d247466e186\"><p class=\"p\">Selection</p></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e162 \"><p class=\"p\">06/30/2001</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e168 \"><p class=\"p\">06/30/2001</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e174 \"><p class=\"p\">10/30/2001</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e180 \"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e186 \"><p class=\"p\">Yes</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e162 \"><p class=\"p\">10/31/2001</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e168 \"><p class=\"p\">06/30/2001</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e174 \"><p class=\"p\">10/30/2001</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e180 \"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e186 \"><p class=\"p\">No</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e162 \"><p class=\"p\">06/15/2001</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e168 \"><p class=\"p\">06/30/2001</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e174 \"><p class=\"p\">10/30/2001</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e180 \"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e186 \"><p class=\"p\">No</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e162 \"><p class=\"p\">10/31/2001</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e168 \"><p class=\"p\">06/30/2001</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e174 \"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e180 \"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e186 \"><p class=\"p\">Yes</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e162 \"><p class=\"p\">06/15/2001</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e168 \"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e174 \"><p class=\"p\">10/30/2001</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e180 \"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e186 \"><p class=\"p\">Yes</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e162 \"><p class=\"p\">10/31/2001</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e168 \"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e174 \"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e180 \"><p class=\"p\">X</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e186 \"><p class=\"p\">Yes</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e162 \"><p class=\"p\">07/01/2001</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e168 \"><p class=\"p\">06/30/2001</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e174 \"><p class=\"p\">10/30/2001</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e180 \"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d247466e186 \"><p class=\"p\">No</p></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section></div>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
